<h2 id="research-interests">Research Interests</h2>
<p>Study of pattern formation in self-organizing systems occurring during phase transformations such as solidification, electrochemical reactions and other transformations with elastic and magneto-elastic coupling.<br />
Development of quantitative phase-field models for different phenomena.<br />
Integration of different modelling techniques.<br /></p>

